Package: dgtf
Type: Package
Title: Variational and Monte Carlo Inference for Bayesian State-Space Models of Count Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "minimeini", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "meini.tang@gmail.com")
    )
Description: Bayesian inference for a general class of state-space models
    for count data, providing a unified interface for variational Bayes and MCMC. 
    Supports univariate observation and state processes, with negative binomial, 
    Poisson, and lognormal families and flexible trend, seasonal, and regression components.
